## Results

| Model | Feature Method | Test Accuracy |
|---|---|---|
| Logistic Regression | Bag of Words | ~57% |
| Logistic Regression | TF-IDF | ~52% |

The BoW model performed better on this dataset. The moderate accuracy is expected — the training set contains only 52 reviews, which is very small by NLP standards. Real-world sentiment analysis models are trained on tens of thousands of examples and typically achieve 85–95% accuracy. All 5 predictions on completely unseen reviews were correct.

